      </a><a href="ESL.English.Listening.Short.Stories/ESL.Listening.Short.Stories.html"><strong>by Stephen King</strong></a></p>
      <p align="left" class="style73"><a href="ESL.English.Listening.Short.Stories/ESL.Listening.Short.Stories.html">'The story centers on Richard Dees, a deeply cynical reporter. Dees' current subject of investigation is the 'Night Flier', an apparent serial killer who travels between small airports in a Cessna Skymaster airplane, gruesomely killing people in a way that leads Dees to think the man is a lunatic who believes himself to be a vampire.</a></p>
